OL,5, Technology aimed at improving safety on
OL,6, all-lane running smart motorways needs 
OL,7, to be improved "urgently", the         
OL,8, transport watchdog has said.           
OL,10,FRadar-based technology meant to improve
OL,11,Fthe detection of stranded vehicles on  
OL,12,Fsmart motorways with no hard shoulder  
OL,13,Fis falling short of targets, the Office
OL,14,Ffor Rail and Road (ORR) said.          
OL,16,FAll-lane motorways are meant to ease   
OL,17,Fcongestion but critics say they have   
OL,18,Fcontributed to deaths.                 
OL,20,FTheir rollout was paused in January.   
